title: Support lf jg or adc duo
body:
I've been playing since 2012 but never really played rank. Looking for bronze - silver players as any higher I'd feel like I'm holding you back.
I main support. I mainly play Thresh-Leona but can play any other support. 
I'm just looking for an adc or jg where we can play some norms and build up our team work 1st then play ranked.

Reply here please

replies.body: Add me if you want ...still learning the game just starting to play ranked but need to get synergy working with someone. I am adc and play ok to well when i have a good support !! Cheers
Sure thing. I'll add you when I'm on next
Meow, im more of a mid main{{champion:55}}  ;-;  but rn, i put adc primary :P coz {{champion:222}} ftw <3
We should play several games with each other! See how we go
